[src:virginia-general-assembly/2000-united-states-state-legislative-elections] All of the seats of the Tennessee House of Representatives and half of the Tennessee Senate were up for election.
[src:virginia-general-assembly/2000-united-states-state-legislative-elections] All of the seats of the Texas House of Representatives and half of the Texas Senate were up for election.
[src:virginia-general-assembly/2000-united-states-state-legislative-elections] Republicans maintained control of the Senate, while Democrats maintained control of the House of Representatives.
