[src:virginia-general-assembly/2000-united-states-state-legislative-elections] Democrats maintained control of the Senate and Republicans won control of the House.
[src:virginia-general-assembly/2000-united-states-state-legislative-elections] All of the seats of the Washington House of Representatives and half of the Washington Senate were up for election.
