[src:virginia-general-assembly/2000-united-states-state-legislative-elections] All of the seats of the American Samoa Senate and the American Samoa House of Representatives were up for election.
[src:virginia-general-assembly/2000-united-states-state-legislative-elections] Members of the Senate serve four-year terms, while members of the House of Representatives serve two-year terms.
[src:virginia-general-assembly/2000-united-states-state-legislative-elections] Gubernatorial and legislative elections are conducted on a nonpartisan basis in American Samoa.
[src:virginia-general-assembly/2000-united-states-state-legislative-elections] All of the seats of the unicameral Legislature of Guam were up for election.
